@newsTitle{Saturday 10 Jan 2004, BSE Sound Archive}

We just opened up the
@uref{beast-doc://browse-bse-files,,BSE Sound Archive}.
Here, users can
@uref{beast-doc://upload-bse-files,, contribute and exchange}
BSE songs, samples or instrument and effect files.
For demonstration purposes, we will also take
@uref{http://www.xiph.org/ogg/vorbis/,, Ogg/Vorbis}
files alongside a BSE Song to ease previews.
For instance, here is the
@uref{http://beast.gtk.org/beast-ftp/bse-files/partymonster.ogg,, Ogg/Vorbis version}
of the BEAST demo song
@uref{http://beast.gtk.org/beast-ftp/bse-files/partymonster.bse,, Party Monster}.

Have fun and
@uref{beast-doc://upload-bse-files,, start contributing}! ;-)


